trans:
Your Civic Service Mission
Objectives
The CADA is committed to an approach known as ‘empowerment building’. This enables everyone to play a part in their own projects and to be at the heart of the decisions that affect them.
Actions
- Promoting culture and access to culture;
- Implementing collective activities and information aimed at facilitating social integration and independent renting;
- Facilitating the volunteer network around learning French and refer people to French courses;
- Developing recreational and cultural activities in conjunction with local facilities (library, etc.);
- Helping people discover the town and its socio-cultural environment, and encouraging them to get involved in local community life (e.g. support for voluntary work);
- Accompanying people to appointments;
- Educational support;
- Internal communication at the CADA (newspaper, creating materials, etc.).
